“DynFaceRestore: Balancing Fidelity and Quality in Diffusion-Guided Blind Face Restoration with Dynamic Blur-Level Mapping and Guidance.”</p>

<p>A heartfelt thank you to Mediatek for supporting our team in completing this research! 🙌💡</p>

<p>📸✨ 我們的研究團隊很榮幸在 ICCV 2025（美國夏威夷）展示我們的研究成果：
「DynFaceRestore：Balancing Fidelity and Quality in Diffusion-Guided Blind Face Restoration with Dynamic Blur-Level Mapping and Guidance」</p>

<p>誠摯感謝 聯發科 對我們研究團隊的支持，協助順利完成這項研究成果！🙌💡</p>

